- Just pass the tape along.
<SYNC Start=472427><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=472605><P Class=ENCC>
He's not right for the part.
<SYNC Start=474436><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=474607><P Class=ENCC>
