<SYNC Start=477075><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=477243><P Class=ENCC>
And that's something<br>
they should learn on their own.
<SYNC Start=479871><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=480046><P Class=ENCC>
Just tell Joey<br>
