<SYNC Start=484439><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=484617><P Class=ENCC>
Then you're the good guy,<br>
and they're the bad guy.
<SYNC Start=487051><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=487220><P Class=ENCC>
That's good. I liked it, they didn't.
<SYNC Start=490121><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=491991><P Class=ENCC>
